年落成。2009年4月20日，香港政府宣布暫時擱置計劃；然而旅遊事務署表示仍然在研究此項目，至2016年底南港島綫通車後才能夠落實發展。為了配合未來計劃的發展的落實，旅遊事務署決定以傳統漁村風貌為主題，先行在香港仔港灣兩岸進行改善工程，同時探討其他長遠方案。"},{"pid":"af77abb330bba6aff032196df3006f24a0f8fee6","tid":2299912,"uid":297609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T07:49:15.000Z","msg":"海洋館捉魚，即煮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbebe9f3fc733de243d2c611a997fd9489906185","tid":2299912,"uid":109982,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"51c551749f3678e2bf1b9c7485e4a68a713059b3","tid":2299912,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"dfa6acb0c6a8e4f2c60d72aa6b983b6f5cf857b6","tid":2299912,"uid":228894,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T06:11:52.000Z","msg":"所謂持份者應該唔包括我地呢啲住南區嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T06:18:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T07:57:56.000Z","msg":"黨鐵都通埋咁耐埋, 原來重有人唔知邊度係鴨脷洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0061e34fd326b4d7f8465f954d256979ede8884","tid":2299912,"uid":142067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"68f5f6525b7b329d4e0a555c3922feb19a8b6535","tid":2299912,"uid":15812,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T06:35:21.000Z","msg":"去水族館簡海鮮<br />\n<br />\n簡岩邊隻就叫個保育員潛水落去捉上黎<br />\n<br />\n現場即開即煮<br />\n<br />\n諗起都正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T08:03:52.000Z","msg":"水族館簡海鮮 <br />\n應該會爆場大把生意 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全球第一間水族館海鮮市場"},{"pid":"34bd0924ea7d1b7c35b494346ed8b23add65daba","tid":2299912,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T08:11:21.000Z","msg":"港島南海鮮市場暨公園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" 